text: We had the simple lunch. The curry chicken with fluffy rice is a delightful dish that is well-balanced and full of rich spices. The deep savory flavors are perfectly blended, making it a satisfying meal that is sure to please any palate. The fluffy rice adds a perfect texture to the dish, making it a must-try for any food lover.
Buy food for breaking fast. Muslim stall. A lot of food selling there. Reasonable price.

Sleepy coffeeshop in industrial park inside Toa Payoh.
Plenty car park with good selection of beer. The 3 stalls in operation seems to cater to quite a decent palate.
Plenty seating space.
The coffee shop only good when you want to find a quiet place to sit down during lunch time.
Go ahead and get it your best. Treat yourself with goodness and foodstuffs .
